sourcesContent: import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import '../css/Table.css' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { useHttp } from '../hooks/http.hook' import { useMessage } from '../hooks/message.hook' function TableSystem({ _id, name, gateway, createdAt, hanldeVidjet }) { const message = useMessage() const { loading, request, error, clearError } = useHttp() useEffect(() => { message(error) clearError() }, [error, message, clearError]) const url = "http://localhost:5000/api/systems" const deleteHandler = (id) => { hanldeVidjet(id) } return ( {name} {gateway} {createdAt} ) } export default TableSystem
